Tutorial.bunny.step1: What just happened? Am I dreaming?  This is such a beautiful place! I wonder what happens if I merge these shiny ladles together
Tutorial.wheat_3_tutorial.step1_1: This place is teeming with life! I can't wait to explore it. Okay, first thing first, let's merge these leaves and see what happens
Tutorial.wheat_3_tutorial.step1_2: Easy-peasy, we can do this all day. Let's try again just to make sure it works.
Tutorial.wheat_3_tutorial.step2_1: By the looks of it, we can get potatoes with these plants. Okay, let's merge these and see what we get next!
Tutorial.wheat_3_tutorial.step2_2: Let’s move this potato plant closer together so we can merge them !
Tutorial.wheat_3_tutorial.step3: Progress! Let's merge these plants and get ready for a harvest!
Tutorial.dishes_0.step1: Look! Look! The Potatoes are ready! Let's harvest them and make baked potatoes. I have just the right recipe.
Tutorial.dishes_0.step2: That's a lot of potatoes! Let's pick them up and get them ready!
Tutorial.dishes_0.step3: Splendid! Here comes one serving of Loaded Baked Potatoes !
Tutorial.dishes_0.step4: The baked potatoes is just a small preview of what I, a future culinary master, can do!
Tutorial.dishes_0.step5: Chef hats! This is what we need to unlock and explore more areas and ingredients!
Tutorial.dishes_0.step6: Here we go! Let's find out what adventures await!
Tutorial.woodsource_1.step1: So you want to be a grand chef? Let's first build you a grand kitchen and restaurant! Chop chop! Time waits for no one.
Tutorial.woodsource_1.step2: Good, let's collect these wood and we are on our way to that world-class restaurant.
Tutorial.woodsource_1.step2_2: Let's merge these chopped woods to create wood panels
Tutorial.woodsource_1.step3: Now, let's clear this plot of land to make room for something spectacular.
Tutorial.woodsource_1.step4: Psst, I have a secret power that can speed up this whole chopping business. Let's give it a try!
Tutorial.woodsource_1.step5: A treasure chest? Your luck really has improved after you met me !
Tutorial.woodsource_1.step6: Let's see what's in the chest!
Tutorial.woodsource_1.step7: Pro tip, we can merge 5 chopped woods together for 2 wood panels. This is what I call productivity increase!
Tutorial.woodsource_1.step8: More chef hats! The more I earn and collect, the more land I can unlock!
